quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  81,1,jab Sooraj lapait liya jaye ga
  81,2,jab tarre be noor ho jayen ge
  81,3,aur jab pahar chalaye jayen ge
  81,4,aur jab bayanay wali ontniyan be car ho jayen gi
  81,5,aur jab wehshi janwar jama ikathay ho jayen ge
  81,6,aur jab darya aag ho jayen ge
  81,7,aur jab roohein ( badnon se ) mila di jayen gi
  81,8,aur jab larki se jo zindah dafna di gayi ho poocha jaye ga
  81,9,ke woh kis gunah par mari gayi
  81,10,aur jab ( amlon ke ) daftar khole jayen ge
  81,11,aur jab asmano ki khaal khech li jaye gi
  81,12,aur jab dozakh ( ki aag ) bharkayi jaye gi
  81,13,aur bahisht jab qareeb layi jaye gi
  81,14,tab har shakhs maloom kar le ga ke wohkiya le kar aaya hai
  81,15,hum ko un sitaron ki qasam jo peechay hatt jatay hain
  81,16,( aur ) jo sair karte aur gayab ho jatay hain
  81,17,aur raat ki qasam jab khatam honay lagti hai
  81,18,aur subah ki qasam jab namodaar hoti hai
  81,19,ke be shak yeh ( quran ) frishta aali maqam ki zabaan ka pegham hai
  81,20,jo sahib qowat maalik arsh ke haan ounchay darjay wala hai
  81,21,sardar ( aur ) amanat daar hai
  81,22,aur ( mukkay walo ) tumahray Rafeeq ( yani Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) deewany nahi hain
  81,23,be shak unhon ne is ( farishtay ) ko ( aasman ke khulay yani ) mashriqi kinare par dekha hai
  81,24,aur woh posheeda baton ( ke zahir karne ) mein bukheel nahi
  81,25,aur yeh shetan mardood ka kalaam nahi
  81,26,phir tum kidhar ja rahay ho
  81,27,yeh to Jahan ke logon ke liye nasiyaat hai
  81,28,( yani ) is ke liye jo tum mein se seedhi chaal chalna chahay
  81,29,aur tum kuch bhi nahi chaah satke magar wohi jo khuday-e rab alameen chahay
